OL,3,CGirl 'complained of headache' before
OL,4,Ccouple's holiday park deaths
OL,6,FA teenage girl complained of a
OL,7,Fheadache before she and her boyfriend
OL,8,Fdied from suspected carbon monoxide
OL,9,Fpoisoning at a holiday park, their
OL,10,Finquest has heard.
OL,12,FCherish Bean, 15, and Ethan Slater,
OL,13,F17, were found dead in a cabin at
OL,14,FLittle Eden Holiday Park in
OL,15,FBridlington last month.
OL,17,FAn inquest opening into the couple's
OL,18,Fdeaths on Tuesday heard they had been
OL,19,Fon a family holiday, and had both been
OL,20,F"fit and well" when the family spent
OL,21,Fthe evening together on 17 February.
OL,26,@|D@AOU|D@NO]
