CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773249076
OL,3,CGirl 'complained of headache' before
OL,4,Ccouple's holiday park deaths
OL,6,FSenior coroner Prof Paul Marks said
OL,7,FCherish left the family at about 9pm
OL,8,Ffor a smaller cabin, known as the "man
OL,9,Fcave", where she was staying with
OL,10,FEthan.
OL,12,FShe returned about an hour later
OL,13,Fcomplaining of a headache, and had
OL,14,Fsome Calpol because the family had no
OL,15,Fparacetamol, the hearing at Hull
OL,16,FCoroner's Court was told.
OL,18,FAfter returning to bed she texted her
OL,19,Fmother after 10pm to say goodnight,
OL,20,FProf Marks said. Ethan went back to
OL,21,Fthe cabin at a similar time.
OL,26,@pD@cOUqD@EO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773249076
OL,3,CGirl 'complained of headache' before
OL,4,Ccouple's holiday park deaths
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Ben Robinson, of
OL,7,FHumberside Police, said four people
OL,8,Fwho are "associated with the
OL,9,Fmanagement and maintenance" of the
OL,10,Fholiday park had been arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of gross negligence
OL,12,Fmanslaughter, interviewed and bailed.
OL,14,FAsked by the coroner whether there was
OL,15,Freason to believe the couple's deaths
OL,16,Fwere "associated with carbon monoxide
OL,17,Fpoisoning", Mr Robinson said there was.
OL,26,@pD@IOUqD@[O]xD@FOUyD@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773249076
OL,3,CGirl 'complained of headache' before
OL,4,Ccouple's holiday park deaths
OL,6,FHe told the hearing that the official
OL,7,Fmedical cause of death was still
OL,8,Fpending the forensic pathologist's
OL,9,Fexamination.
OL,11,FMr Robinson said the boiler from the
OL,12,Fcabin had been recovered and a
OL,13,Fforensic evaluation had been done,
OL,14,Fsupported by specialist gas engineers.
OL,16,FHe said the Health and Safety
OL,17,FExecutive and the National Crime
OL,18,FAgency had also been consulted.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
