FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1773249076
OL,3,CGirl 'complained of headache' before
OL,4,Ccouple's holiday park deaths
OL,6,FProf Marks adjourned the inquest until
OL,7,Fafter the conclusion of the police
OL,8,Finvestigation.
OL,10,FHe said: "I would like, once again, to
OL,11,Fextend my condolences to both the
OL,12,Ffamilies of these young people."
OL,14,FIn a tribute to her daughter released
OL,15,Fby police last month, Cherish's mother
OL,16,Fdescribed her as "my perfect girl, my
OL,17,Fangel".
OL,19,FEthan's mother said he was "the most
OL,20,Fbeautiful young man to walk the earth".
OL,26,@rD@JOUtD@`O]xD@ROU
